 Installation :
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

 Just extract Gui4Doom.lha in your Doom directory ;-)


What you need :
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

 You already know that you need ADoom, or AmigaDoom, or
DoomAttack or PsiDoom ;-)

 You need these commands in C:

  -dir    ( From the Workbench disk !!! ) 3440 octets
  -rename 
  -copy                                  
  -execute                                     
  -addbuffers
  -mount


